{"tid":1891884,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"驅散學運民眾被控殺人未遂，馬英九出庭應訊","createTime":"2020-02-22T07:13:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-22T11:07:14.000Z","uid":52658,"like":36,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e5b742000f0f24b1ec4fd88f816bf3a41682cac9","tid":1891884,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T07:13:26.000Z","msg":"〔記者溫于德／台北報導〕台北地院更二審審理「太陽花學運」期間「323佔領行政院」遭警方強制驅離案，今再度開庭並傳喚被告時任總統馬英九、行政院長江宜樺、警政署長王卓鈞、中正一分局長方仰寧。馬英九今仍否認犯罪，針對法院勘驗當天畫面則無意見，但馬的律師吳柏宏要原告律師指名畫面中民眾是否為本案原告，否則與本案無關。<br />\n<br />\n發生在2014年間的「323佔領行政院」案，參與抗爭的7旬老翁周榮宗（已故）等23名受傷掛彩民眾，自訴控告馬英九等4人涉殺人未遂、重傷害未遂、傷害、強制等罪。"},{"pid":"8aad2af7ee29a3a57b2dacdb18eca6d7d29835f1","tid":1891884,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T07:25:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f38e356c34e14c596ac91ada2472da85e75abf97","tid":1891884,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T08:00:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb473b6131f2c48df0701c03020e7088a34a6e82","tid":1891884,"uid":53498,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T08:14:23.000Z","msg":"香港幾時先可以捉班狗官曱甴去審<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好撚葡萄"},{"pid":"6488ed224ab26914956a65bdbda734acd35b085e","tid":1891884,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T08:15:14.000Z","msg":"奶共九"},{"pid":"4d067eecf7b52644fc728dcac422e80fe5b08c00","tid":1891884,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T08:16:13.000Z","msg":"希望入到<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"552eb37f5af189aaff205e292b06dae3c7335064","tid":1891884,"uid":224479,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"ci